    "Section 5: Discussion: From reactive to proactive AI governance?",
    "Governance is probably one of the areas that most clearly demonstrate how challenging it has become to create respected and legitimate regulation in an increasingly complex and diverse society, where perceptions of respect, fairness, sustainability, and justice constantly shift (Taylor, 2023).",
